Movie Ticket Booking App

This is a simple web application for booking movie tickets. The app allows users to view movie details, see a list of available movies, and purchase tickets for a selected movie.

*Features

- View details of the first movie on the homepage, including poster, title, runtime, showtime, and available tickets.
- See a menu of all movies on the left side of the page.
- Purchase tickets for a movie, with a real-time update of available tickets on the frontend.